---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Placeholder from '@components/Placeholder/Placeholder.astro';

const title = 'Placeholder';
---

<BaseLayout title={title}>
  <div class="docs-page">
    <nav><a href="/docs/test_pages/">&larr; Test Pages</a></nav>
    <div class="prose">
      <h1>Placeholder</h1>

      <p>A light-purple box with a dark-purple outline and a centered label. Used to stand in for layout elements (header, footer, announcement banner) while their real implementations are under construction. Dark mode swaps the two purples.</p>

      <h2>Properties</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Property</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><code>name</code></td><td><code>string</code></td><td>(required)</td><td>The label text rendered inside the placeholder</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>class</code></td><td><code>string</code></td><td>&mdash;</td><td>Optional extra class applied to the root element</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Examples</h2>

      <h3>Named label</h3>
      <Placeholder name="HEADER" class="placeholder-demo--short" />
      <Placeholder name="ANNOUNCEMENT BANNER" class="placeholder-demo--short" />
      <Placeholder name="FOOTER" class="placeholder-demo--tall" />

      <p>The announcement banner, header, and footer all have real implementations now under <code>src/components/AnnouncementBanner/</code>, <code>src/components/Header/</code>, and <code>src/components/Footer/</code>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .docs-page {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
  }

  h1 {
    border-bottom: var(--border-width-thick) solid var(--color-border-strong);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .placeholder-demo--short {
    height: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .placeholder-demo--tall {
    height: 120px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
</style>
